Interface MoleculeIterators.MoleculeInterface

MoleculeComponent
Enclosing interface:
MoleculeIterators
public static interface MoleculeIterators.MoleculeInterface

Classes that have AtomIteratorInterface interface that enumerates atoms, and BondIteratorInterface interface that enumerates bonds. These classes can be handled together where only these iterators are necessary from the molecules.
